ne of the players in the liquefied petroleum gas transportation sector, showed remarkable financial</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108442571/image_108442571.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742893-stealthgas-stock-growing-firm-offering-a-prime-buying-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 17:42:39"}, {"id": "4742869", "title": "Is ZIM Integrated A Buy After The Ex-Dividend Date?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"3d rendering of question mark made up of dollar banknotes on blue background.\" data-id=\"1178728033\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Gearstd</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Is ZIM Integrated A Buy After The Ex-Dividend Date?</h2> <p><span>We previously covered </span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4724982-zim-integrated-double-tailwinds-trigger-robust-near-term-dividend-prospects\">ZIM Integrated Shipping</a><span> (NYSE:</span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ZIM\" title=\"ZIM Integrated Shipping Services Ltd.\">ZIM</a></span><span>) in October 2024, discussing why we had upgraded the stock to</span><span> a speculative buy for dividend oriented investors, thanks to</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742869-is-zim-integrated-a-buy-after-the-ex-dividend-date", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 17:30:00"}, {"id": "4742847", "title": "Brookfield Renewable Partners: One Of My Highest Conviction Investments", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"USA, Arkansas, Beaver Lake Dam, elevated view\" data-id=\"200457452-001\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Wesley Hitt/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I have been bullish on Brookfield Renewable Partners L.P. Limited Partnership Units (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BEP#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" title=\"Brookfield Renewable Partners L.P. Limited Partnership Units\">BEP</a>) since my initial <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4680278-brookfield-renewable-partners-discounted-6-percent-yielder-that-is-subject-to-growth\">thesis</a> back in May, 2024. While BEP has recently struggled in terms of lifting its share price higher, my</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742847-brookfield-renewable-partners-one-of-my-highest-conviction-investments", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 17:15:07"}, {"id": "4742872", "title": "Adobe: Heading Into Q4, Two Key Ingredients Are Missing", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Adobe headquarters in San Jose, California, USA\" data-id=\"1581810849\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Adobe (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ADBE\" title=\"Adobe Inc.\">ADBE</a></span>) is set to report its fourth-quarter results this upcoming Wednesday, December 11th, after market close.</p> <p>Although shares have recovered from their May bottom, Adobe is closing in on a disappointing 2024.</p> <h2>Introduction To Adobe</h2> <p>Adobe is one of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1581810849/image_1581810849.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742872-adobe-heading-into-q4-two-key-ingredients-are-missing", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 17:00:55"}, {"id": "4742890", "title": "Okta: On The Path To A Rebound, Keep Holding On For Upside", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"OKTA headquarters in SOMA district, San Francisco\" data-id=\"1169876053\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6138px\" height=\"4094px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Sundry Photography</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Good value is hard to find in today\u2019s markets, and many investors, including myself are growing increasingly jittery on sky-high valuations. For that reason, investing in \u201cgrowth at a reasonable price,\u201d especially in stocks that haven\u2019t yet ridden a big momentum bump this</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742890-okta-on-the-path-to-a-rebound-keep-holding-on-for-upside", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 16:31:18"}, {"id": "4742845", "title": "Constellation Brands: Reflecting Both The Weakness And Potential In Beverages", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Hands of man and women toasting beer at music festival\" data-id=\"1904538649\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Dear readers/followers,</p> <p>One of my primary investments for the past year has been investment into the beverage and alcohol sector. This has been the case with companies such as Diageo (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DEO\" title=\"Diageo plc\">DEO</a>) and giants like LVMH (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742845-constellation-brands-reflecting-weakness-and-potential-in-beverages", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 16:30:00"}, {"id": "4742887", "title": "STAG Industrial: Use The Pullback To Your Advantage", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"phrase buy the dip handwritten on night wet window glass surface\" data-id=\"1289941019\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5472px\" height=\"3648px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">z1b</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>STAG Industrial (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/STAG\" title=\"STAG Industrial, Inc.\">STAG</a></span>) is a unique pick operating within the industrial properties sector as a triple net lease player. As of September 30, 2024, the Company had 578 properties featuring 114.5 sq. ft. across 40 states. Its properties serve mostly Air Freight &amp; Logistics, Containers &amp; Packaging, and Automobile</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742887-stag-industrial-use-the-pullback-to-your-advantage", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 16:15:51"}, {"id": "4742833", "title": "Rubrik: Raising My Price Target As Momentum Picks Up, But Don't Get Greedy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219304815/image_1219304815.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Rubrik Headquarters\" data-id=\"1219304815\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219304815/image_1219304815.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219304815/image_1219304815.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219304815/image_1219304815.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219304815/image_1219304815.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219304815/image_1219304815.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219304815/image_1219304815.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219304815/image_1219304815.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219304815/image_1219304815.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">hapabapa</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>One way to characterize the market in 2024 is that it has been a winner-take-all market, where momentum-driven stocks (especially those with AI ties) enjoyed massive gains and others with slowing growth potential quickly wore out investors' patience. I continue to advocate for</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219304815/image_1219304815.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742833-rubrik-raising-my-price-target-as-momentum-picks-up-but-dont-get-greedy", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 16:00:00"}, {"id": "4742882", "title": "Will The Long Awaited Breakout For Esperion Therapeutics Hold?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1647029659/image_1647029659.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Medium shot senior male patient sitting on bed in hospital room\" data-id=\"1647029659\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1647029659/image_1647029659.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1647029659/image_1647029659.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1647029659/image_1647029659.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1647029659/image_1647029659.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1647029659/image_1647029659.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1647029659/image_1647029659.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1647029659/image_1647029659.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1647029659/image_1647029659.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Thomas Barwick/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Suddenly, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4715605-esperion-therapeutics-delivering-on-expectations-while-navigating-overhangs\">the weight of the overhangs</a> for Esperion Therapeutics (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ESPR\" title=\"Esperion Therapeutics, Inc.\">ESPR</a></span>) got a little lighter. The stock made an important technical achievement by breaking out above a year-long trading range. This important validation of </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1647029659/image_1647029659.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742882-will-the-long-awaited-breakout-for-esperion-therapeutics-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 15:43:11"}, {"id": "4742891", "title": "Wall Street Week Ahead", "description": "<div class=\"wsb_wrapper\"> <div class=\"wsb_main\"><span><p class=\"wsb_pb\"><strong>Listen on the go! A daily podcast of Wall Street Breakfast will be available by 8:00 a.m. on <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/wall-street-breakfast?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=toptext&amp;utm_campaign=wsbpodpromo\">Seeking Alpha</a>, <a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/wall-street-breakfast/id1358381502\" rel=\"nofollow\">iTunes</a>, <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/05uLjJxkVgQsRk8LWLCLpx\" rel=\"nofollow\">Spotify</a>.</strong></p></span></div> <figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img alt=\"\" data-id=\"1733234018\" data-type=\"getty-image\" height=\"864px\" src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" width=\"1536px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Boy Wirat</p></figcaption></picture></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div>\n<div class=\"wsb_section\"><div class=\"wsb_mb\"> <p class=\"wsb_pb\"> </p> <p class=\"wsp-pb\"> </p> <p class=\"wsp-pb\"> </p> <p>The Fed pendulum swings back to the inflation part of the mandate this week. The November consumer price index hits on Wednesday, just a week before the FOMC's final 2024 meeting.<br><br>Economists expect that headline and core CPI, which excludes food and energy, rose 0.3% last month. In addition, the headline producer price index, which is due Thursday, rose 0.3%, with the core PPI up 0.2%.<br><br>Last week's November payrolls was a Goldilocks number for those hoping for a December rate cut: solid, but not enough to derail the Fed's easing path. The odds of a quarter-point cut rose to 86%.<br><br>Among the big names reporting earnings this week are Oracle (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ORCL\" title=\"Oracle Corporation\">ORCL</a>), Adobe (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ADBE\" title=\"Adobe Inc.\">ADBE</a>), Broadcom (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVGO\" title=\"Broadcom Inc.\">AVGO</a>), Costco Wholesale (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COST\" title=\"Costco Wholesale Corporation\">COST</a>), Toll Brothers (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TOL\" title=\"Toll Brothers, Inc.\">TOL</a>) and Ciena (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CIEN\" title=\"Ciena Corporation\">CIEN</a>).<br><br>The Goldman Sachs U.S. Financial Services Conference starts Tuesday, and the Barclays 22nd Annual Global Technology Conference begins Wednesday.</p> <p class=\"wsp-pb\"> </p> <p class=\"wsp-pb\"> </p> <p><b>Earnings spotlight:</b> Monday, December 9 - Oracle (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ORCL\" title=\"Oracle Corporation\">ORCL</a>), Toll Brothers (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TOL\" title=\"Toll Brothers, Inc.\">TOL</a>), and Casey\u2019s General Stores (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CASY\" title=\"Casey's General Stores, Inc.\">CASY</a>). <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\">See the full earnings calendar</a>.<br><br><b>Earnings spotlight:</b> Tuesday, December 10 - AutoZone (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AZO\" title=\"AutoZone, Inc.\">AZO</a>), Ferguson Enterprises (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FERG\" title=\"Ferguson Enterprises Inc.\">FERG</a>), GameStop (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GME\" title=\"GameStop Corp.\">GME</a>), Ollie\u2019s Bargain Outlet Holdings (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OLLI\" title=\"Ollie's Bargain Outlet Holdings, Inc.\">OLLI</a>), and Academy Sports and Outdoors (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ASO\" title=\"Academy Sports and Outdoors, Inc.\">ASO</a>). <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\">See the full earnings calendar</a>.<br><br><b>Earnings spotlight: </b>Wednesday, December 11 - Adobe (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ADBE\" title=\"Adobe Inc.\">ADBE</a>). <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\">See the full earnings calendar</a>.<br><br><b>Earnings spotlight:</b> Thursday, December 12 - Broadcom (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVGO\" title=\"Broadcom Inc.\">AVGO</a>), Costco Wholesale (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COST\" title=\"Costco Wholesale Corporation\">COST</a>), and Ciena (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CIEN\" title=\"Ciena Corporation\">CIEN</a>). <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\">See the full earnings calendar</a>.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"wsb_section\"><div class=\"wsb_mb\"> <p class=\"wsb_bold\">In Case You Missed It ...</p> <p class=\"wsp-pb\"> </p> <div class=\"before_last_paragraph-piano-placeholder\"></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4362670-markets-stocks-why-you-should-be-checking-reddit-again-ahead-of-trading-meme\">Why you should be checking Reddit again ahead of trading</a><br><br><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4371397-wells-fargos-core-list-googl-dis-hd-wmt-and-more\">Wells Fargo\u2019s \u2018Core\u2019 List</a><br><br><a href=\"https://s